## ğŸš€ Features

### ğŸ‘©â€ğŸ’¼ Admin Panel
- Manage all registered cafÃ© users  
- Assign or change subscription plans (`Basic` or `Professional`)  
- Deactivate users  
- View system stats  

### ğŸ§¾ Basic Plan
- Sales management and invoice generation  
- Simple inventory (in/out stock updates)  
- Basic financial reports (daily / weekly / monthly)  
- One connected receipt printer (browser print)  

### ğŸ’¼ Professional Plan
- Includes all Basic features  
- Advanced inventory (low-stock alerts, expiration, reorder level)  
- Full accounting (ledger, balance sheet, profit/loss, expenses)  
- Customer loyalty (points, discounts, auto rewards)  
- Analytical charts (top products, busy hours)  
- Automatic daily backup  
- Server-side printing (IPP protocol)  
- Email support  

---

## ğŸ–¨ï¸ Printing System

| Plan | Type | Description |
|------|------|--------------|
| Basic | Browser print | Uses `window.print()` for local printing |
| Professional | Server-side | Sends PDF via IPP (Internet Printing Protocol) to a configured printer |

**PDF invoices** are generated using `puppeteer` or `pdf-lib` and stored in `/public/invoices/`.

